### Get all specialties
GET http://localhost:3000/api/specialties
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single specialty by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/specialties/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new specialty
POST http://localhost:3000/api/specialties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cardiología"
}

###

### Update a specialty
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/specialties/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Neurología"
}

###

### Delete a specialty
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/specialties/1
